                                    <% } %>

                                    <h6><br>Sample Levels available now!</h6>

                              </div>
                         </div>

                    </div>
               </div>
     </section>

<div style="height: 7px; background-color: #EAEFF5"></div>

  <% if(data.success == false){ %>
     <section class="signup section" id="signup">
          <div class="container">
               <div class="row">

                   <div class="mb-lg-0 mb-4 col-lg-5 col-md-10 mx-auto col-12">
                       <h2 class="mb-4 text-white">Sign Up</h2>
                       <% if(data.hasOwnProperty("account_made") && (data.account_made == false)){ %>
                         <div class="alert alert-danger">
                            <strong>Sign up unsuccesful!</strong> <%= data.message %>
                          </div>
                          <% } %>

                       <form action="/signup" method="post" class="contact-form webform" role="form" id="signup-form">
                         <input required type="text" class="form-control" name="fname" placeholder="First Name">
                         <input required type="text" class="form-control" name="lname" placeholder="Last Name">
                         <input required type="text" class="form-control" name="email" placeholder="Email ID">
                         <input required type="text" class="form-control" name="username" placeholder="Display name">
                         <input required type="password" class="form-control" name="password" placeholder="Password">

                          <button type="submit" class="form-control submit-button" id="signup-submit" name="submit">Sign Up</button>
                       </form>
                   </div>

                    <div class="ml-auto col-lg-5 col-md-6 col-12">
                        <h2 class="mb-4 text-white">Log In</h2>
                        <% if(data.hasOwnProperty("logged_in") && (data.logged_in == false)){ %>
                          <div class="alert alert-danger">
                             <strong>Log in unsuccesful!</strong> <%= data.message %>
                           </div>
                           <% } %>
                           <form action="/login" method="post" class="contact-form webform" role="form" id="login-form">

                               <input required type="text" class="form-control" name="email" placeholder="Email">
                               <input required type="password" class="form-control" name="password" placeholder="Password">
                               <button type="submit" class="form-control submit-button" id="login-submit" name="submit">Log In</button>

                           </form>
                    </div>


               </div>
          </div>
     </section>

 <% } %>

<div style="height: 7px; background-color: #EAEFF5"></div>
          <!-- CLASS -->
          <section class="feature" id="rules">
            <div class="container" >
                <div class="row">

                    <div class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-center ml-lg-auto mr-lg-5 col-lg-5 col-md-6 col-12">
                        <h2 class="mb-3 " style="color:var(--primary-color);">Rules of the game</h2>

                        <!-- <h6 class="mb-4 text-white">Some o</h6> -->
                        <ul class="text-white">
                            <li>Only open to University students in HK, it is recommended to use your university mail ID to register
                            </li>
                          <li>Use the clues and riddles scattered in the pages to find the answer to the levels
</li>
                          <li>The page source, level title, favicon and image names are some of the additional places to always look for clues </li>
                          <li>You shall need to make the most use of the internet to help you find the solutions to the levels
</li>
                          <li>Freely available online tools such as cipher decoders, photo editors, steganography tools will be of help during this hunt</li>

                          <li>The format for answering is replacing the levelname in the URL with the solution you procured. For example if the answer to the level with url mystiko.xyz/levels/sample0 is answer42 then to get to the next level, change the url to mystiko.xyz/levels/answer42 </li>
                          <li>This is a single-player game.  Players who wish to play in teams should do so using a single account. If players are suspected of cheating by sharing answers, they shall be removed from the game.</li>
                          <li>The first player to complete all levels wins.</li>
                          <li>May the best player win!</li>

                        </ul>

                        </div>

                    <div class="mr-lg-auto mt-3 col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
                         <div class="about-working-hours">
                              <div>

                                    <h2 class="mb-4" style="color:var(--primary-color);">Event timeline</h2>

